<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased API Latencies and Management Console Error Rates>
We are investigating increased API latencies and increased error rates for the RDS Management Console in the US-EAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased API Latencies and Management Console Error Rates>
Between 8:21 AM and 10:01 AM PDT, we experienced increased API latencies and increased error rates for the RDS Management Console in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
